  "text": [
    "Despair leaves",
    "a dry spot",
    "the passage of light",
    "through my veins.",
    "I fail as a celibate.",
    "The smell of honey",
    "fills my throat.",
    "I lose touch with",
    "my bone when",
    "it stiffens.",
    "Sometimes",
    "I find a place",
    "to spring",
    "& spike you",
    "while you cry.",
    "I try to rev things up",
    "although I hate",
    "the sound of flying.",
    "Gagging leaves",
    "the breath",
    "no exit.",
    "Then the chest puffs out,",
    "no longer hapless,",
    "in the face of",
    "everything aloof",
    "& distant,",
    "where the world begins.",
    "I go on craving",
    "hostile to the ones like you",
    "who bind me.",
    "I surrender any",
    "knowledge of the cave",
    "in which I hide",
    "from light."
  ],
  "title": "I Fail As a Celibate",
  "year": ""
}